00:23:16.320 --> 00:23:20.130
&gt;&gt; Krista L. Cox: Just because
108 has been such a focus

00:23:20.130 --> 00:23:24.470 position:56%
of this discussion so far, you know,
I just want to say that, you know,

00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:27.390
there have been some criticisms
