00:45:11.940 --> 00:45:14.270
It's just too sweeping.

00:45:14.270 --> 00:45:18.690 position:56%
And the combination of no obligation
on the person that's protected

00:45:18.690 --> 00:45:20.860
and the fact that everything
is automatically protected,

00:45:20.860 --> 00:45:23.390
those things collectively
create a lot of problems.

00:45:23.390 --> 00:45:24.690
&gt;&gt; Kevin Amer: OK.

