00:45:49.300 --> 00:45:51.180
And it just doesn't
go to litigation.

00:45:51.180 --> 00:45:52.480
And then, second--

00:45:52.480 --> 00:45:53.780
&gt;&gt; Regan Smith: Can I interrupt?

00:45:53.780 --> 00:45:55.540
